title: Bobby's Celebrity Phone Numbers + Kip Moore Quarantining In The Mountains + Raymundo’s Toilet Paper Trick + Easy Bible Trivia

description:
Bobby has Amy guess which celeb's phone numbers he has in his phone, which celeb's houses he’s been to and his celebrity elevator list. Kip Moore calls in from his quarantine spot in the mountains. Raymundo shares a guaranteed to get toilet paper. Plus, we play 'Easy Bible Trivia' in honor of Easter weekend!
